# Macheseinfach defaults

- **Runtime:** Bun — use `bun run`, `bun test`, `bun install` from repo root.
- **UI:** `@macheseinfach/ui` (Gumroad-inspired tokens) — extend primitives before one-off styles.
- **Secrets:** SOPS + age — never commit `.env`, `.kounds/age.key`, or cleartext credentials.
- **License:** PolyForm Noncommercial — no commercial redistribution without explicit permission.
- **Plans:** Non-trivial changes → `docs/plans/YYYY-MM-DD-<slug>.md` before large diffs.
